content: ai16z-demirix: Focused on significant development work, opening two substantial PRs: elizaos/eliza#5634, which makes API keys optional for `npx elizaos create`, and elizaos/eliza#5633, which targets the project directory for `.elizadb`. This work involved modifying 328 files with a net addition of over 16,000 lines of code, primarily focused on new features and bug fixes.
